<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>季節の手料理屋 吟家</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Yuji+Boku&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= yield :head %>

    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
    <link rel="icon" href="/icon.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="icon" href="/icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icon.png">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
  </head>

  <body>

    <header class="header">
      <div class="header-container">
        <h1 class="header-logo">吟家</h1>

        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><%= link_to t('header.home'), root_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to t('header.about'), about_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to t('header.menu'), dishes_list_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to t('header.news'), news_list_path %></li>
          
          <li><%= link_to t('header.reserve'), "https://l.instagram.com/?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres-reserve.com%2Fja%2Frestaurants%2Fginyamishuku&e=AUDwHLicpddAoYuTEuXBcAEYPqq7bSA3Qpg8diDMjiytN5buOoe2agI6EOCv4GWMEX92vGB_YEag3rFcb_Cs9he1a9wb7e1Ttme4g7Kf5G9mIg6op-I1e6LA_Jv1JbgPAZrQFnT_75TKM2zoakPzmL8Utvw", class: "btn-reserve" %></li>
          <div class="lang-dropdown" id="langDropdown">
            <button class="lang-btn" type="button">
              Language <span class="arrow"></span>
            </button>
            
            <ul class="lang-menu">
              <li><a href="?locale=ja" class="active">日本語</a></li>
              <li><a href="?locale=en">English</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <%= yield %>

      <div class="access-section">
        <div class="access-container">
          
          <div class="access-info">
            <h3 class="access-shop-name">季節の手料理屋 吟家</h3>
            <p class="access-text"><span>【住所】東京都世田谷区池尻 3-13-2 秀和ハウス1F</p>
            <p class="access-text"><span>【交通アクセス】東急田園都市線「池尻大橋駅」西口 徒歩10分</p>
            <p class="access-text"><span>【電話】050-5593-3031</p>
            <p class="access-text"><span>【営業時間】<br>火・水・木・金・土<br>18:00 〜 25:00（L.O. 料理24:00 ドリンク24:30）<br>日・祝日<br>18:00 〜 23:00（L.O. 料理22:00 ドリンク22:30）<br>ランチ〈日曜限定〉<br>12:00〜14:00（L.O.13:30）</p>
            <p class="access-text"><span>【定休日】月曜日</p>
          </div>

          <div class="access-map" style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px; max-width: 500px; height: 300px;">
            <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3242.0817682812885!2d139.6781973!3d35.650357!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x6018f4a779315555%3A0xedff276cab56adf8!2z5ZCf5a62!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1781167214922!5m2!1sja!2sjp" width="500" height="350" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>        
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>

      <div class="black-footer-bar">
        <div class="footer-bar-container">
          
          <div class="footer-bar-logo">
            季節の手料理屋 吟家
          </div>

          <ul class="footer-bar-menu">
            <li><%= link_to "ホーム", root_path %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "吟家について", about_path %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "おしながき", dishes_list_path %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "お知らせ一覧", news_list_path %></li>
          </ul>

          <div class="footer-bar-copyright">
            <%= link_to "© 2026 吟家. All Rights Reserved.", new_food_path, class: "hidden-admin-link" %>          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

  </body>

</html>
